{"about_the_game":"Expand your Just Cause 4 experience with the Expansion Pass. Includes new weapons, missions, gear and gameplay! <br />\r\n<br />\r\nGrants 7 days' early access to each of the three expansions upon their release:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDare Devils of Destruction: Drive one of many weaponized vehicles as you take on rival gangs across multiple explosive challenges<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLos Demonios: An ancient demonic force is unexpectedly released upon the Island of Solis. Rico must now tackle a new type of threat and seek out answers to send the demons back from whence they came before it\u2019s too late!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDanger Rising: Armed with a new prototype hover board, Rico vows to take down the Agency after learning of their plans to eliminate him.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868424/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728485439","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868424/page.bg.jpg?t=1728485439","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868424/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728485439","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868424/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728485439","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id":21},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Trading Cards","id":29},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>Just Cause\u2122 4: Danger Rising</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868424/extras/JC4_Danger_Rising_In-Text_Banner_ENG.png?t=1728485439\" /><br>Armed with a new prototype hover board, Rico vows to take down the Agency after learning of their plans to eliminate him.<br> <br>Tom Sheldon joins Rico on his mission and the pair begin by investigating a large submarine which has surfaced ominously off the coast of Solis. <br> <br>Could Rico be out of his depth against The Agency? The odds are mounting and the hunter is about to become the hunted\u2026<br><br>Danger Rising is included in the Just Cause 4 Expansion Pass<br><br>Early Access begins 29th August for Gold Edition and Expansion Pass owners. Available to purchase separately and play from 5th September.</p><br><h1>Just Cause\u2122 4: Los Demonios</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868424/extras/JC4_Los_Demonios_Capsule_in-text_banner.jpg?t=1728485439\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After investigating a newly discovered temple an ancient demonic force is accidentally released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now Rico must tackle a new threat and send the demons back from whence they came before it\u2019s too late!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Early Access begins 26th June for Gold Edition and Expansion Pass owners. Available to purchase separately and play from 3rd July.</p></p><br><h1>Just Cause\u2122 4: Dare Devils of Destruction</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868424/extras/JC4_DDoD_Capsule_In-text_banner.jpg?t=1728485439\" /><br>Rico Rodriguez gears up for an adrenaline fuelled adventure in Dare Devils of Destruction. <br>Drive one of many weaponized vehicles as you take on rival gangs across three explosive challenges. Burn rubber and shred metal in this celebration of violent vehicular mayhem.<br><br>Destroy. Drive. Survive.<br><br>Dare Devils of Destruction is included in the Just Cause 4 Expansion Pass</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Expand your Just Cause 4 experience with the Expansion Pass. Includes new weapons, missions, gear and gameplay! <br><br>Grants 7 days' early access to each of the three expansions upon their release:<br><br>Dare Devils of Destruction: Drive one of many weaponized vehicles as you take on rival gangs across multiple explosive challenges<br><br>Los Demonios: An ancient demonic force is unexpectedly released upon the Island of Solis. Rico must now tackle a new type of threat and seek out answers to send the demons back from whence they came before it\u2019s too late!<br><br>Danger Rising: Armed with a new prototype hover board, Rico vows to take down the Agency after learning of their plans to eliminate him.","developers":["Avalanche Studios"],"fullgame":{"appid":"517630","name":"Just Cause 4 Reloaded"},"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868424/header.jpg?t=1728485439","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"JUST CAUSE 4 \u00a9 2018 Square Enix Ltd.  All rights reserved. <br />\r\nDeveloped by Avalanche Studios AB. <br />\r\nJust Cause, EIDOS, the EIDOS logo, SQUARE ENIX and the SQUARE ENIX logo are registered trademarks or trademarks of the Square Enix group of companies. Avalanche and the Avalanche logo are trademarks of Fatalist Entertainment AB.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256759098,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256759098/movie480.mp4?t=1565883653","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256759098/movie_max.mp4?t=1565883653"},"name":"PEGI EN - Danger Rising","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256759098/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1565883653","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256759098/movie480.webm?t=1565883653","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256759098/movie_max.webm?t=1565883653"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256754549,"mp4":{"480":